OL,3,CHouseholds braced for 'awful April' as
OL,4,Ccouncil tax and water bills soar
OL,6,FHouseholds are facing near across-the-
OL,7,Fboard increases in their bills as yet
OL,8,Fanother "awful April" takes effect.
OL,10,FWhile energy bills are falling ` for
OL,11,Fthe time being at least ` hikes to
OL,12,Fcouncil tax, water, broadband and
OL,13,Fmobile phone costs are threatening to
OL,14,Fstretch many households to breaking
OL,15,Fpoint, charities have warned.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
