OL,3,CHouseholds braced for 'awful April' as
OL,4,Ccouncil tax and water bills soar
OL,6,FAcross England, the average Band D
OL,7,Fcouncil tax in 2026/27 will be #2,392
OL,8,F` an increase of #111 or 4.9% on 2025-
OL,9,F26, according to the Ministry of
OL,10,FHousing, Communities & Local
OL,11,FGovernment.
OL,13,FThe figures include all additional
OL,14,Fcharges, including adult social care,
OL,15,Fparish precepts and costs levied by
OL,16,Fpolice, fire and regional authorities
OL,17,Fwhere appropriate.
OL,19,FIt is the fourth year in a row that
OL,20,Fthe England-wide increase has averaged
OL,21,Faround 5%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
