OL,3,CHouseholds braced for 'awful April' as
OL,4,Ccouncil tax and water bills soar
OL,6,FHousehold water bills across England
OL,7,Fand Wales are to rise by an average of
OL,8,F5.4%, equating to #33 a year for the
OL,9,Faverage household.
OL,11,FThere is significant regional
OL,12,Fvariation in bill increases, with
OL,13,FSevern Trent customers seeing a 10%
OL,14,Fincrease, Sutton and East Surrey
OL,15,Fimposing an 11% increase, Bristol
OL,16,FWater a 12% rise and Affinity Water
OL,17,F(central region) customers warned they
OL,18,Fhave a 13% jump coming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
