OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774929839
OL,3,CHouseholds braced for 'awful April' as
OL,4,Ccouncil tax and water bills soar
OL,6,FAround 2.5 million households are
OL,7,Feligible for social tariffs, with
OL,8,Fsavings of around 40%.
OL,10,FA host of broadband providers are
OL,11,Fhiking prices by almost #50 per year,
OL,12,Fwith one in four customers (28%) free
OL,13,Fto leave and already paying between #7
OL,14,Fand #9 a month more than in-contract
OL,15,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
